0Ram%26quot%3B%20slogans%20would%20hurt%20the%20religious%20feelings%20of%20any%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20were%20charged%20under%20the%20IPC%20Section%20295A%20for%20allegedly%20raising%20'Jai%20Shri%20Ram'%20slogans%20in%20a%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20also%20booked%20under%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20Sections%20447%20(criminal%20trespass)%2C%20505%20(statements%20conducing%20to%20public%20mischief)%2C%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%2C%2034%20(common%20intention)%20and%20295A%20(outraging%20religious%20feelings).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20noted%20that%20the%20complainant%20in%20the%20case%20had%20himself%20said%20that%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20were%20living%20in%20harmony%20in%20the%20concerned%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPermitting%20of%20further%20proceedings%20against%20the%20petitioners%20would%20become%20an%20abuse%20of%20process%20of%20law%2C%20the%20bench%20underlined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%2C%20the%20bench%20said%20any%20and%20every%20act%20will%20not%20become%20an%20offence%20under%20Section%20295A%20of%20the%20IPC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20charged%20that%20the%20accused%20persons%20had%20barged%20inside%20the%20mosque%20on%20September%2024%2C%202023%2C%20at%20about%2010.50%20p.m.%20and%20raised%20slogans%20of%20%26quot%3BJai%20Shri%20Ram%26quot%3B.%20They%20were%20also%20charged%20with%20threatening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20complaint%20was%20registered%20the%20accused%20were%20shown%20as%20unknown%20persons%20and%20later%20the%20accused%20were%20taken%20into%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20challenging%20the%20allegations%20against%20them%2C%20the%20accused%20filed%20an%20appeal%20before%20the%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20and%20quashed%20the%20case%20in%20this%20regard%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20complainant%20mentioned%20that%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20lived%20in%20harmony%20in%20the%20area%20and%20also%20claimed%20shouting%20%26quot%3BJai%20Shri%20Ram%26quot%3B%20slogans%20would%20flare%20up%20communal%20tension.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729043580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fcourt-generic_625x300_1527245477936.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchanting-jai-shri-ram-in-mosque-doesnt-hurt-religious-feelings-karnataka-high-court-6799300%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20quashed%20the%20criminal%20case%20lodged%20by%20the%20police%20against%20two%20persons%20in%20connection%20with%20allegedly%20raising%20%26quot%3BJai%20Shri%20Ram%26quot%3B%20slogans%20inside%20a%20mosque.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chandan%20Taparia%20of%20MOFSL%20recommends%20buying%20these%20three%20stocks%20on%20Oct%2016%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729043177000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-04%2F04%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1680624965-149.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fchandan-taparia-of-mofsl-recommends-buying-these-three-stocks-today-124101600059_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Oberoi%20Realty%20has%20broken%20out%20of%20a%20consolidation%20zone%20and%20is%20headed%20up%20with%20higher-than-average%20buying%20volumes%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fchandan-taparia-of-mofsl-recommends-buying-these-three-stocks-today-124101600059_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--st