n%20is%20a%20cryptographer%20and%20former%20senior%20research%20scientist%20at%20MIT%2C%20who%20said%20he%20also%20avoids%20Microsoft%20and%20Google%20products%20because%20of%20his%20concerns%20about%20keeping%20his%20data%20secure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Apple%20representatives%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20about%20this%20story.%20Each%20company%20has%20previously%20said%20it%20takes%20privacy%20and%20security%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flearn.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fwindows%2Fsecurity%2Fintroduction%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintroduction%20to%20Windows%20security%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20last%20updated%20in%20July%2C%20Microsoft%C2%A0said%20that%20its%20Windows%2011%20operating%20system%20was%20developed%20with%20a%20%26quot%3BZero%20Trust%20security%20model%20based%20on%20the%20premise%20that%20no%20person%20or%20device%20anywhere%20can%20have%20access%20until%20safety%20and%20integrity%20is%20proven.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20July%202024%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcloud.google.com%2Fdocs%2Fsecurity%2Foverview%2Fwhitepaper%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecurity%20overview%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Google%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSecurity%20drives%20our%20organizational%20structure%2C%20culture%2C%20training%20priorities%2C%20and%20hiring%20processes%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20%26quot%3Bprioritized%20in%20the%20way%20we%20handle%20customer%20data%2C%20our%20account%20controls%2C%20our%20compliance%20audits%2C%20and%20our%20certifications.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fguide%2Fsecurity%2Fintro-to-apple-platform-security-seccd5016d31%2Fweb%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplatform%20security%20overview%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20updated%20in%20May%2C%20stated%20that%20security%20is%20designed%20%26quot%3Binto%20the%20core%20of%20its%20platforms.%26quot%3B%20The%20compan