times.com%2F2024%2F04%2F06%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-giants-harvest-data-artificial-intelligence.html%3Fsmid%3Dnytcore-ios-share%26sgrp%3Dc-cb%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20has%20reportedly%20used%20YouTube%20content%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOodles%20of%20other%20websites%20and%20content%20have%20been%20used%20for%20AI%20training%20as%20part%20of%20the%20open-source%20dataset%20called%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcommoncrawl.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECommon%20Crawl.%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20This%20could%20have%20already%20included%20Photobucket%20images%20hosted%20on%20other%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeonard%20said%20Photobucket%20is%20in%20talks%20with%20several%20companies%20to%20license%20the%20images.%20Rather%20than%20a%20one-shot%20deal%20where%2C%20say%2C%20OpenAI%20gets%20images%20to%20use%20forever%2C%20the%20potential%20deals%20are%20generally%20for%20a%20few%20years%20and%20for%20specific%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20company%20will%20come%20to%20us%20and%20say%2C%20'We%20need%20content%20of%20%3Cem%3Elandscapes%20with%20people%20in%20a%20distance%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20we're%20looking%20for%20%3Cem%3Ebeach%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Emountains%3C%2Fem%3E%2C'%26quot%3B%20Leonard%20explained.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20say%2C%20'OK%2C%20great.%20Based%20on%20that%20request%2C%20we%20have%20150%2C000%20images%20that%20we%20can%20license%20you.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhotobucket%20estimates%20about%20half%20of%20its%2013%20billion%20images%20are%20public%20and%20eligible%20for%20AI%20licensing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b1ca6dbf-d446-4b92-9ca0-9dc53af83ed5%5C%22%3ENotifying%20users%20about%20the%20new%20Terms%20of%20Service%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELeonard%20said%20Photobucket%20sent%20an%20email%20in%20July%20to%20its%20customers%20alerting%20them%20to%20an%20update%20to%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fphotobucket.com%2Flegal%2Fbiometric-information-privacy-policy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETerms%20of%20Service%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20update%20outlined%20how%20public%20images%20may%20be%20used%20for%20AI%20training%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bscanning%20and%20processing%20of%20the%20Public%20User%20Uploaded%20Content%2C%20including%20extracting%20physical%20features%2C%20e.g.%20measurements%2C%20of%20your%20Biometric%20Information%20(e.g.%2C%20face%2C%20iris%2C%20etc.)%2C%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20machine%20learning%20training.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20an%20old%20Photobucket%20account%20from%20around%202007%20that%20I%20used%20for%20hosting%20images%20for%20an%20old%20blog.%20For%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20I've%20gotten%20emails%20with%20increasingly%20dire%20warnings%20that%20my%20account%20was%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20deactivated.%20(It%20hasn't%20been.)%20At%20some%20point%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20had%20already%20downloaded%20the%20images%20and%20stored%20them%20elsewhere%2C%20so%20I%20wasn't%20too%20concerned.%20(I%20do%20continue%20to%20pay%20%2410%20a%20month%20for%20my%20old%20personal%20photos%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthis-quote-perfectly-sums-up-how-yahoo-is-killing-everything-it-buys-2014-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFlickr%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresumably%2C%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20people%20like%20me%20with%20an%20old%20Photobucket%20account%2C%20largely%20forgotten%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0maybe%20abandoned%20because%20we%20moved%20the%20photos%20somewhere%20else%20or%20simply%20didn't%20care.%20And%20then%20there's%20another%20group%20of%20people%20who%20aren't%20even%20getting%20these%20emails%3A%20Maybe%20they%20signed%20up%20with%20a%20student%20email%20that%20they%20can't%20access%20anymore%2C%20or%20maybe%20they%20long%20ago%20forgot%20their%20username%20and%20password%20combination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeonard%20said%20Photobucket%20has%20been%20attempting%20to%20reach%20customers%20through%20email%2C%20on-site%20alerts%2C%20and%20other%20methods%20(including%20alerting%20users%20in%20the%20press%2C%20like%20in%20this%20story).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20receive%20the%20email%20from%20Photobucket%20alerting%20me%20about%20the%20new%20policy%2C%20but%20like%20most%20other%20emails%20about%20updated%20Terms%20of%20Service%2C%20I%20simply%20didn't%20bother%20opening%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20kind%20of%20a%20two-way%20street%20where%20if%20you%20put%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20personal%20memories%20on%20the%20site%2C%20maybe%20you%20should%20do%20your%20best%20to%20continue%20to%20update%20the%20email%20address%20and%20everything%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Leonard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotobucket-my-photos-images-licensed-ai-training-account-how-to-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729032281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670eb26da7031864928234fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotobucket-my-photos-images-licensed-ai-training-account-how-to-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Remember%20that%20old%20Photobucket%20account%3F%20You%20might%20want%20to%20log%20in.%20The%20public%20photos%20could%20soon%20be%20licensed%20to%20train%20AI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotobucket-my-photos-images-licensed-ai-training-account-how-to-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bus%2C%20train%20%26amp%3B%20air%20services%20hit%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20capital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729031967000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114263980%2Cimgsize-1361056.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofin