de%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20engineer%20recognized%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-jaguar-all-electric-self-driving-cars-i-pace-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJaguar%20I-PACE%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Waymo's%20choice%20of%20electric%20vehicle%20for%20its%20autonomous%20fleet%2C%20had%20a%20limited%20range.%20Jaguar%20advertises%20a%20range%20of%20up%20to%20246%20miles%20for%20the%20I-PACE.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20account%20for%20the%20cameras%2C%20GPUs%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bbeefy%20computers%26quot%3B%20attached%20to%20Waymo's%20fleet%20that%20likely%20take%20up%20battery%20power%2C%20Tung%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Tung%20said%20she%20prepared%20for%20a%2024-hour%20haul%20by%20carrying%20multiple%20cameras%20with%20extra%20batteries%2C%20making%20a%20bathroom%20run%20before%20her%20trip%2C%20and%20eating%20high-carb%2C%20low-dairy%20snacks%20that%20would%20not%20overstimulate%20her%20digestive%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Waymo%20was%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ealso%20limited%20to%20local%20roads%20within%20the%20city%20limits%20of%20San%20Francisco%2C%20which%20is%20less%20than%2050%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esquare%20miles.%20The%20company%20also%20restricts%20riders%20to%20four%20stops%20before%20passengers%20must%20step%20out%20and%20request%20a%20new%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20circumvent%20this%2C%20Tung%20said%20she%20would%20edit%20her%20journey%20mid-ride%20to%20direct%20the%20Waymo%20to%20different%20parts%20of%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20before%20the%20Waymo%20reached%20a%20stop%2C%20Tung%20said%20she%20would%20input%20a%20new%20destination%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKarp%20said%20the%20company%20is%20now%20%26quot%3Bexploring%26quot%3B%20limiting%20the%20number%20of%20times%20users%20can%20edit%20their%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a8d9ca0d-38ed-4520-b9f4-56f17407c428%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWaymo's%20limit%3