0the%20cars%20she%20requested%20had%20a%20charge%20of%2080%25%20or%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKarp%20wrote%20that%20the%20company%20adopted%20the%20industry%20standard%20of%20charging%20to%2080%25%20to%20maximize%20the%20life%20span%20of%20the%20car's%20battery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Waymo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670c76ce6ac7b701e7cabfcc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWaymo's%20dashboard%20during%20Sophia%20Tung's%20ride%20showed%20an%20alert%20to%20recharge%20the%20vehicle.%3Cp%3ESophia%20Tung%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20car%20reached%20an%20estimated%20range%20of%2020%20miles%20left%2C%20Tung%20said%20the%20Waymo%20ended%20the%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20certainly%20didn't%20realize%20how%20tired%20the%20ride%20was%20making%20me%20feel%20until%20I%20stepped%20out%20of%20the%20car%20after%20six%20and%20a%20half%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20legs%20sort%20of%20just%20gave%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKarp%20said%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Blonger%20personal%20trips%2C%20but%20the%20Waymo%20Driver%20can%20operate%20for%20far%20longer%20without%20a%20disengagement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20San%20Francisco%20resident%2C%20Tung%20said%20Waymo%20isn't%20her%20main%20mode%20of%20transportation.%20But%20she'll%20give%20the%20company%20some%20props.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20witnessed%20all%20of%20that%2C%20I'm%20more%20inclined%20to%20trust%20Waymo's%20driving%20more%20than%20even%20my%20own%20driving%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-ride-six-hours-longest-youtube-sf-san-francisco-robotaxi-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729029823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com