0in%20its%20stupidity%20was%20pressuring%20him%20at%20such%20a%20time.%20So%20John%20said%20to%20me%2C%20'Should%20I%20sign%20this%20contract%3F'%20and%20I%20said%2C%20'Of%20course%20you%20should%20sign%20this%20contract.'%20He%20said%2C%20'Why%3F'%20I%20said%2C%20'Because%20I%20wrote%20it'%20%E2%80%94%20which%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%20wasn't%20true.%20But%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20get%20him%20to%20sign%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrillstein%2C%20who%20was%20managing%20Michaels%2C%20said%20that%20Belushi%20agreed%20to%20sign%20the%20contract%20if%20he%20decided%20to%20manage%20him%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20swear%20to%20God%2C%20it%20was%20five%20minutes%20before%20showtime%2C%26quot%3B%20Brillstein%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFiction%3A%20Lorne%20Michaels%20ordered%20a%20llama%20for%20an%20opening%20night%20skit.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nicholas%20Braun%20and%20a%20llama%20in%20%26quot%3BSaturday%20Night.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67097a5ea703186492816613%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENicholas%20Braun%20as%20Andy%20Kaufman%20and%20a%20llama%20in%20%26quot%3BSaturday%20Night.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ESony%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20in%20the%20movie%2C%20a%20llama%20arrives%20at%20the%20studio%20because%20Michaels%20preferred%20that%20animal%20over%20a%20donkey%20for%20a%20segment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aforementioned%20books%20make%20no%20mention%20of%20a%20llama%20being%20present%20backstage%20on%20the%20night%20of%20the%20series%20premiere.%20The%20llama's%20inclusion%20in%20the%20film%20is%20most%20likely%20a%20nod%20to%20a%20long-running%20joke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFans%20who%20have%20tuned%20in%20to%20the%20sketch%20comedy%20series%20for%20years%20know%20that%20when%20the%20camera%20goes%20backstage%2C%20there's%20usually%20a%20llama%2C%20a%20showgirl%2C%20or%20someone%20dressed%20like%20Abraham%20Lincoln%20loitering%20in%20the%20hallway%20for%20no%20logical%20reason.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vanityfair.com%2Fhollywood%2F2016%2F09%2Fsaturday-night-live-llama-showgirl-lincoln-eugene-lee-backstage-secrets-interview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVanity%20Fair%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20former%20writer%20and%20Weekend%20Update%20anchor%20Seth%20Meyers%20popularized%20this%20gag%20during%20his%20time%20on%20the%20show.%20But%20even%20further%20back%2C%20Eric%20Idle%20might%20have%20been%20responsible%20for%20the%20running%20joke%20when%20he%20hosted%20the%20show%20in%20the%20'70s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20why%20we%20do%20it%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20production%20designer%20Eugene%20Lee%20told%20VF%20in%202016.%20%26quot%3BWe%20get%20a%20script%20%5Bset%5D%20in%20the%20hallway%2C%20so%20we%20call%20the%20prop%20department%20and%20say%2C%20'Order%20up%20a%20llama.'%20Sometimes%20it's%20the%20wrong%20llama%20%E2%80%94%20it%20has%20the%20wrong%20color.%20We%20send%20it%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFiction%3A%20The%20lighting%20rig%20fell%20dangerously%20close%20to%20Belushi%20and%20Gilda%20Radner%20mid-rehearsal%2C%20setting%20the%20couch%20on%20fire.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Matt%20Wood%20as%20John%20Belushi%20and%20Ella%20Hunt%20as%20Gilda%20Radner%20in%20%26quot%3BSaturday%20Night.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670993253f2165d716e07352%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221029%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMatt%20Wood%20as%20John%20Belushi%20and%20Ella%20Hunt%20as%20Gilda%20Radner%20in%20%26quot%3BSaturday%20Night.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ESony%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EReitman%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Fentertainment%2Fmovies%2F2024%2F10%2F11%2Ffact-check-saturday-night-snl%2F75459263007%2F%5C%22%20target%3