kward%20in%20front%20of%20the%20camera.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20real%20life%2C%20Chase%20was%20already%20set%20to%20be%20the%20%26quot%3BWeekend%20Update%26quot%3B%20anchor%20prior%20to%20the%20series%20premiere%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202014%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2014%2F06%2Florne-michaels-exclusive-interview-emmys-2014-saturday-night-live-late-night-tv-787797%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeadline%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Michaels%20said%20that%20he%20participated%20in%20the%20sketch's%20%26quot%3Bearliest%20presentation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20as%20we%20got%20closer%20to%20the%20air%20show%2C%20I%20began%20to%20realize%20that%20I%20didn't%20think%20I%20could%20be%20the%20person%20who%20cut%20other%20people's%20pieces%20and%20left%20my%20own%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Michaels%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20gave%20'Weekend%20Update'%20to%20Chevy%2C%20who%20was%20not%20a%20cast%20member%2C%20but%20a%20writer%20at%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichaels%20and%20some%20of%20the%20cast%20members%2C%20including%20Chase%2C%20had%20a%20screen%20test%20on%20September%2017%2C%201975%2C%20to%20run%20through%20the%20material%20and%20see%20how%20it%20translated%20on%20camera.%20During%20that%20screen%20test%2C%20Chase%20read%20the%20jokes%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BWeekend%20Update%26quot%3B%20and%20nailed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFact%3A%20Rosie%20Shuster%20likened%20Lorne%20Michaels%20to%20a%20stray%20dog.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222752%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rachel%20Sennott%20as%20Rosie%20Shuster%20and%20Gabriel%20LaBelle%20as%20Lorne%20Michaels%20in%20%26quot%3BSaturday%20Night.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67099192a7031864928179f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221552%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERachel%20Sennott%20as%20Rosie%20Shuster%20and%20Gabriel%20LaBelle%20as%20Lorne%20Michaels%20in%20%26quot%3BSaturday%20Night.%26qu