20politics%20of%20vote-bank%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Canada%20are%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20worst-ever%20diplomatic%20spat%20in%20the%20history%20of%20bilateral%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%20India%20has%20recalled%20its%20high%20commissioner%20to%20Canada%20and%20expelled%20six%20top%20diplomats%20from%20Canada%20yesterday.%20Canada%20mirrored%20India's%20move.%20The%20reason%20-%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20proximity%20to%20the%20Khalistan%20separatist%20movement%20and%20his%20sympathy%20towards%20declared%20terrorists%20and%20extremists%20who%20spread%20hate%2C%20violence%2C%20and%20extremism%20on%20Canadian%20soil%20-%20all%20to%20appeal%20to%20his%20vote%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trudeau%2C%20who%20is%20seeking%20another%20term%20as%20Canada's%20prime%20minister%2C%20but%20facing%20one%20setback%20after%20another%20politically%20in%20his%20country%2C%20has%20repeatedly%20supported%20the%20Khalistani%20separatist%20movement%20and%20allowed%20space%20for%20them%20to%20operate%20by%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bfreedom%20of%20speech%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fglorification-of-violence-india-slams-canada-over-khalistani-floats-5611239%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20of%20Canada%20has%20stood%20shoulder-to-shoulder%20with%20terrorists%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20extremists%20and%20separatists%20by%20attending%20Khalistan%20rallies%20in%20Canada.%20By%20doing%20so%2C%20Canada's%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20directly%20violated%20India's%20national%20security%20concerns%20whilst%20also%20violating%20India's%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20by%20supporting%20those%20who%20want%20another%20nation%20to%20be%20carved%20out%20of%20India%20-%20terming%20all%20this%20as%20%26quot%3Bfree%20speech%20in%20Canada.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCelebration%20and%20glorification%20of%20violence%20should%20not%20be%20a%20part%20of%20any%20civilized%20society.%20Democratic%20countries%20which%20respect%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20should%20not%20allow%20intimidation%20by%20radical%20elements%20in%20the%20name%20of%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%26quot%3B%20India%20had%20said%20about%20Trudeau's%20attendance%20at%20the%20Khalistan%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20his%20concern%20over%20grave%20situation%20and%20rapidly%20deteriorating%20ties%2C%20while%20also%20seeing%20a%20rise%20in%20extremist%20elements%20in%20Canada%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20had%20said%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20%26quot%3BBy%20allowing%20political%20space%20to%20Khalistani%20separatist%20elements%2C%20the%20Canadian%20government%20(led%20by%20Justin%20Trudeau)%20is%20repeatedly%20showing%20that%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcanada-showing-its-vote-bank-is-more-powerful-than-its-rule-of-law-s-jaishankar-5631952%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evote%20bank%20is%20more%20powerful%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20its%20rule%20of%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia%20respects%20and%20practices%20freedom%20of%20speech%2C%20but%20that%20does%20not%20equate%20with%20freedom%20to%20threaten%20foreign%20diplomats%2C%20extend%20support%20to%20separatism%20or%20allow%20political%20space%20to%20elements%20advocating%20violence%20and%20terror.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20had%20also%20wondered%20how%20people%20with%20%26quot%3Bdubious%20backgrounds%20are%20being%20allowed%20to%20enter%20and%20live%20in%20Canada%26quot%3B%2C%20referring%20to%20select%20Khalistani%20separatists%20among%20the%20Sikh%20migrants%20from%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20any%20rules-based%20society%2C%20you%20would%20imagine%20that%20you%20would%20check%20people's%20background%2C%20how%20they%20came%2C%20what%20passport%20they%20carried%20etc%2C%26quot%3B%20he