%20courtesy%20greeting%20as%20Mr%20Sharif%20welcomed%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20for%20the%20official%20dinner%20for%20SCO%20leaders.%20Few%20worlds%20were%20spoken%20during%20the%20interaction%20that%20lasted%20less%20than%20twenty%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETies%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20have%20nearly%20been%20non-existent%20in%20the%20last%20decade%20since%20Pak-based%20terrorists%20targeted%20Indian%20military%20establishments%20in%20a%20series%20of%20terror%20attacks%20in%202015%20and%202016.%20India%2C%20which%20has%20for%20long%20aimed%20for%20peace%20and%20stability%20in%20the%20region%2C%20has%20made%20it%20amply%20clear%20to%20Pakistan%20that%20%26quot%3Bterror%20and%20talks%20cannot%20go%20hand-in-hand%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bdialogue%20and%20diplomacy%20can%20only%20move%20forward%20in%20an%20environment%20free%20of%20terrorism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENEARLY%20A%20DECADE%20OF%20NO%20DIALOGUE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar's%20visit%20to%20Pakistan%20is%20the%20first%20by%20an%20Indian%20minister%20in%20nearly%20ten%20years.%20The%20last%20visit%20by%20an%20Indian%20foreign%20minister%20was%20when%20Mr%20Jaishankar's%20predecessor%2C%20Sushma%20Swaraj%2C%20had%20visited%20Islamabad%20for%20a%20conference%20on%20Afghanistan.%20Mr%20Jaishankar%2C%20who%20was%20then%20the%20foreign%20secretary%20had%20accompanied%20the%20then%20minister%20on%20her%20official%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESushma%20Swaraj's%20visit%20was%20followed%20in%20quick%20succession%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20pushed%20for%20peace%20in%20the%20region%20by%20taking%20the%20initiative%20and%20giving%20a%20surprise%20visit%20to%20then%20Pakistani%20prime%20minister%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20at%20his%20ancestral%20home.%20But%20despite%20sincere%20efforts%20by%20India%2C%20talks%20were%20yet%20again%20derailed%20by%20a%20series%20of%20terror%20attacks%20on%20Indian%20soil%20by%20terrorists%20harboured%20and%20sheltered%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20he%20reached%20Islamabad%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20New%20Delhi%20that%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20neighbouring%20country%20was%20only%20for%20the%20SCO%20summit%20and%20that%20no%20bilateral%20talks%20with%20Islamabad%20will%20be%20taking%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%7C%20%3Cstrong%3EWatch%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20NDTV%20World%20Summit%20on%20October%2021-22.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspecial.ndtv.com%2Fndtv-world-summit-2024-167%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGet%20All%20The%20Details%20Here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLike%20with%20any%20neighbour%2C%20India%20would%20certainly%20like%20to%20have%20good%20relations%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20but%20that%20cannot%20happen%20by%20overlooking%20cross-border%20terrorism%20and%20indulging%20in%20wishful%20thinking.%26quot%3B%20The%20decision%20to%20send%20the%20senior%20minister%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20which%20is%20the%20host%20nation%20for%20the%20SCO%20Summit%20this%20time%2C%20is%20seen%20purely%20as%20a%20display%20of%20India's%20commitment%20to%20the%20forum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20is%20hosting%20the%20two-day%20SCO%20Council%20of%20Heads%20of%20Government%20(CHG)%20summit%20on%20October%2015%20and%2016.%20%26quot%3BThe%20SCO%20CHG%20meeting%20is%20held%20annually%20and%20focuses%20on%20the%20trade%20and%20economic%20agenda%20of%20the%20Organisation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20had%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729011360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F0m8abo38_s-jaishankar-shehbaz-sharif-ani_625x300_15_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdecade-of-no-dialogue-then-a-20-second-greeting-india-pakistan-de-hyphenated-6797302%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22S%20Jaishankar%2C%20who%20is%20in%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20Shanghai%20Coo