ive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Ram%20Gopal%20Varma%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20tweeted%20about%20him%20and%20it%20got%206%20million%20views.%20That%20is%20just%20an%20indication%20of%20what%20kind%20of%20interest%20he%20arouses%20in%20public%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20public%20is%20always%20fascinated%20by%20dons%2C%20which%20is%20why%20we%20make%20films...%20So%20I%20think%20he%20is%20getting%20a%20cult%20following%2C%20which%20is%20a%20very%20very%20new%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tweet%20is%20question%20is%20one%20where%20Mr%20Varma%20sums%20up%20the%20story%20so%20far%20of%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%2C%20commenting%20that%20if%20it%20was%20a%20Bollywood%20script%2C%20the%20writer%20would%20have%20been%20thrashed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EA%20LAWYER%20turned%20GANGSTER%20wants%20to%20take%20REVENGE%20for%20a%20DEER'S%20death%20by%20killing%20a%20SUPER%20STAR%20and%20as%20a%20WARNING%20orders%20some%20of%20his%20GANG%20of%20700%20%2C%20which%20he%20recruited%20through%20face%20book%20to%20first%20kill%20a%20BIG%20POLITICIAN%20who%20is%20a%20close%20friend%20of%20the%20STAR%20..%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20POLICE%20can't%20catch%20him%20because...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Ram%20Gopal%20Varma%20(%40RGVzoomin)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRGVzoomin%2Fstatus%2F1845692738882458056%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2014%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawrence%20Bishnoi%20shot%20into%20headlines%20once%20again%20last%20week%20with%20the%20murder%20of%20Maharashtra's%20former%20minister%20Baba%20Siddique%20and%20his%20henchmen's%20threats%20for%20those%20supporting%20Salman%20Khan.%20Baba%20Siddique%20was%20killed%20apparently%20because%20he%20was%20a%20close%20friend%20of%20the%20actor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetails%20have%20emerged%2