0as%20the%20winner%20and%20also%20said%20the%20list%20of%20candidates%20would%20be%20out%20anytime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assembly%20by-elections%20at%20Palakkad%20and%20Chelakkara%20were%20necessitated%20after%20sitting%20legislators%20Shafi%20Paramabil%20(Congress)%20and%20K%20Radhakrishnan%20(CPI-M)%2C%20respectively%2C%20vacated%20the%20seats%20after%20winning%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Wayanad%20parliamentary%20constituency%20fell%20vacant%20as%20the%20winner%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20chose%20to%20retain%20the%20traditional%20family%20borough%20of%20Rai%20Bareli%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20from%20where%20he%20was%20also%20elected.%20The%20Congress%20subsequently%20announced%20his%20sister%20and%20party%20General%20Secretary%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20as%20its%20candidate%20in%20what%20will%20be%20her%20poll%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20is%20all%20set%20to%20be%20on%20Wayanad%2C%20which%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20won.%20Though%20the%20victory%20of%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20seems%20certain%2C%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20is%20if%20she%20will%20better%20her%20brother's%20margin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUDF%20convenor%20MM%20Hassan%20said%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20will%20contest%20all%20the%20seats%2C%20will%20win%203-0%20and%20at%20Chelakkara%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20big%20surprise.%20%26quot%3BIn%20Kerala%2C%20it's%20now%20a%20triangular%20contest%20and%20we%20all%20know%20what%20happened%20at%20the%20Thrissur%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20(where%20BJP%20candidate%20Suresh%20Gopi%20won)%20as%20it%20was%20an%20election%20that%20was%20fixed%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20CPI-M%20and%20that's%20what%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20ruling%20Left%2C%20the%20two%20Assembly%20by-elections%20will%20be%20contested%20by%20the%20alliance%20major%2C%20CPI-M%2C%20while%20the%20Wayanad%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20goes%20to%20the%20CPI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20government%2C%20presently%20caught%20in%20a%20bind%20over%20a%20string%20of%20controversies%2C%20failure%20to%20retain%20the%20Chelakkara%20Assembly%20seat%20will%20hang%20heavy.%20What%20has%20put%20the%20CPI-M%20in%20a%20spot%20of%20bother%20is%20that%20Chelakkara%20is%20a%20reserved%20constituency%20and%20they%20are%20burning%20the%20midnight%20oil%20to%20find%20the%20most%20suitable%20replacement%20for%20Radhakrishnan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENewly-appointed%20Left%20Democratic%20Front%20convenor%20TP%20Ramakrishnan%2C%20however%2C%20dismissed%20the%20present%20wave%20of%20criticism%20against%20the%20state%20government%20by%20pointing%20out%20that%20in%202021%2C%20a%20similar%20situation%20prevailed%20and%20when%20votes%20were%20counted%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20won%20a%20stellar%20victory%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20to%20retain%20office%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20high%20hopes%20in%20Palakkad%2C%20where%20in%20the%202021%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20their%20candidate%20'Metroman'%20E%20Sreedharan%20gave%20a%20fright%20to%20Parambil%20before%20losing%20by%20less%20than%204%2C000%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20BJP%20President%20K.Surendran%20said%20ever%20since%20the%20April%2026%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20on%20a%20high%20and%20it%20will%20now%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20three%20by-elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20list%20of%20candidates%20from%20the%20state%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20national%20party%20and%20very%20soon%2C%20the%20names%20will%20be%20announced.%20We%20wish%20to%20make%20it%20very%20clear%20that%20we%20will%20continue%20our%20winning%20streak%20and%20come%20out%20successful%20in%20the%20two%20Assembly%20by-elections%20and%20at%20Wayanad%2C%20we%20will%20be%20putting%20up%20a%20stiff%20fight%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%