to%20lose.%20The%20machines%20with%2060-70%20per%20cent%20battery%20charge%20are%20the%20ones%20on%20which%20Congress%20won.%20Why%20did%20this%20happen%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Khera%20speaking%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20results%20over%20the%20last%2010-15%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%20it%20can't%20be%20that%20when%20results%20don't%20go%20your%20way%20you%20start%20raising%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EKitna%20dikhayenge%2C%20kaun%20dikhata%20hai%20itna%20bataiye.%20Koi%20ek%20process%20comparative%20bataiye%20poori%20country%20main%20jahan%20public%20disclosure%2C%20disclosure%2C%20disclosure%2C%20participation%2C%20participation%20itna%20adkhik%20ho.%20Koi%20ek%20bataiye%20process%3C%2Fem%3E%20(How%20much%20more%20transparent%20can%20we%20be%2C%20you%20tell%20me.%20Tell%20me%20about%20one%20comparative%20process%20where%20there%20is%20so%20much%20public%20disclosure%20and%20participation.%20You%20show%20me%20one%20process)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728996900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2F91ehru5o_voting-machines-reuters_625x300_08_April_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-jharkhand-assembly-elections-2024-has-single-use-calculator-like-battery-poll-panels-rebuttal-on-evm-charge-6795193%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20much%20more%20transparent%20can%20one%20be%2C%20asked%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20he%20again%20underlined%20that%20the%20EVMs%20or%20voting%20machines%20are%20safe%20and%20robust.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-jharkhand-assembly-elections-2024-has-single-use-calculator-like-battery-poll-panels-rebuttal-on-evm-charge-6795193%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BV