f%20somebody%20touches%20me%20on%20the%20bus%2C%20I%20can%20just%20push%20the%20pin%20back%20on%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20always%20asked%20by%20our%20families%20to%20take%20precautions%20and%20equip%20ourselves%20with%20tools%20that%20could%20help%20us%20navigate%20a%20public%20space.%20This%20was%20just%20part%20of%20existing%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20doctor-turned-artist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20was%20one%20particular%20incident%20about%20seven%20years%20back%20that%20left%20an%20indelible%20mark%20on%20her%20psyche.%20This%20incident%20would%20motivate%20her%20to%20create%20one%20of%20her%20standout%20art%20projects%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3ECecelia%E2%80%99ed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20walking%20on%20the%20street%20in%20HBR%20Layout%20when%20a%20couple%20of%20boys%20walked%20up%20to%20me%20and%20spat%20on%20my%20face.%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20why%20they%20did%20that.%20I%20had%20to%20go%20home%20and%20wash%20my%20face%20and%20T-shirt%2C%20which%20were%20covered%20in%20their%20spit.%20It%20was%20a%20scary%20experience.%20Growing%20up%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20encountered%20so%20many%20incidents%20of%20men%20touching%20and%20groping%20me%20in%20public%20but%20that%20incident%20was%20so%20out%20of%20the%20way.%20I%20just%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20someone%20would%20spit%20on%20me%20for%20no%20apparent%20reason%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIndu-Antony-Navratri-Feature-Image-1728656568.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meet%20the%20artist%20reclaiming%20public%20spaces%20for%20women%20-%20Indu%20Antony%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIndu-Antony-Navratri-Feature-Image-1728656568.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%