betterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-1728467702-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-1728467702-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-1728467702-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369361%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Rani%20and%20Dr%20Abhay%20Bang%20are%20co-founders%20of%20SEARCH%20(Society%20for%20Education%2C%20Action%20and%20Research%20in%20Community%20Health)%20and%20have%20spent%20three%20decades%20working%20with%20tribal%20communities%20in%20Gadchiroli%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20couple%20isn%E2%80%99t%20lauded%20simply%20for%20their%20inventive%20take%20on%20tribal%20healthcare%2C%20but%20also%20their%20culturally%20appropriate%20approaches.%20In%20a%20region%20where%20language%2C%20culture%20barriers%2C%20and%20geographic%20inaccessibility%20pose%20significant%20challenges%2C%20and%20illness%20is%20often%20understood%20through%20spiritual%20beliefs%20and%20traditional%20healing%20practices%2C%20introducing%20modern%20medicine%20required%20thoughtful%20and%20respectful%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20the%20tribes%E2%80%99%20reluctance%20melted%20into%20gratitude%2C%20the%20Bangs%20knew%20they%20were%20on%20the%20right%20path.%20Thirty-nine%20years%20ago%2C%20fresh%20out%20of%20the%20premier%20Johns%20Hopkins%2C%20they%20stood%20at%20the%20precipice%20of%20a%20sea%20of%20opportunities%2C%20each%20more%20lucrative%20than%20the%20other.%20But%2C%20an%20inner%20voice%20guided%20their%20next%20step%20%E2%80%94%20research%20is%20fruitful%20in%20areas%20where%20problems%20exist%2C%20not%20where%20facilities%20are%20ample.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20formed%20the%20backbone%20of%20their%20decision%20to%20head%20to%20the%20naxal-hit%2