o%20treat%20tribal%20communities.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20tribal%20pockets%20across%20India%2C%20high%20infant%20mortality%20rates%20(IMR)%20continue%20to%20perplex%20authorities%3B%20one%20of%20the%20many%20pressing%20issues.%20Studies%20suggest%20that%20over%2089%20percent%20of%20tribal%20women%20have%20anaemia%2C%20while%20only%2070.1%20per%20cent%20of%20tribal%20women%20deliver%20in%20an%20institution.%20Meanwhile%2C%20children%20from%20tribal%20communities%20were%20found%20to%20be%20almost%20one%20and%20a%20half%20times%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20underweight%20than%20children%20from%20other%20communities.%20This%20owes%20to%20malnourished%20expectant%20mothers%2C%20a%20study%20found%2C%20whose%20findings%20revealed%20that%20only%2025%20percent%20of%20pregnant%20and%20lactating%20tribal%20women%20had%20adequate%20protein%20and%20calorie%20intake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20biggest%20killer%20is%20misinformation%2C%20Dr%20Rani%20remarked%20through%20her%20years%20of%20work%20with%20women%20in%20Gadchiroli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20four%20major%20issues%20that%20I%20have%20seen%20women%20here%20face%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F143287%2Fup-menstruation-padman-school%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenstrual%20problems%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reproductive%20tract%20infections%20that%20are%20manifested%20in%20the%20form%20of%20white%20discharge%2C%20uterine%20cancers%2C%20and%20infertility%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Rani%20shares.%20She%20spotlights%20the%20gaps%20and%20potential%20solutions%20that%20will%20better%20healthcare%20outcomes%20in%20tribal%20belts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAddress%20the%20gap%20in%20knowledge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMisinformation%20is%20benign%20until%20it%E2%80%99s%20not.%20As%20Dr%20Rani%20discovered%2C%20the%20cultural%20chasms%20of%20health%20are%20deep-rooted.%20Her%20conversations%20with%20wome