d.%20Prasanna%20Gettu%20suggests%20five%20ways%20to%20foster%20a%20culture%20of%20respect%2C%20equality%2C%20accountability%2C%20and%20working%20towards%20creating%20a%20society%20where%20violence%20is%20not%20tolerated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F369214%2Fprasanna-gettu-helps-domestic-violence-survivors-rebuild-lives-suggests-ways-to-end-crime-abuse-in-india%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Million%20Farmers%20to%208000%20Schools%3A%20How%203%20Startups%20Are%20Writing%20India%E2%80%99s%20Growth%20Story%20in%20Villages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20This%20article%20features%20portfolio%C2%A0companies%20of%20Elevar%20Equity%2C%20which%C2%A0is%20also%20an%20investor%20in%20The%20Better%20India.%20Editorial%20integrity%20and%20transparency%20remain%20our%20priority%2C%20and%20this%20piece%20has%20been%20written%20independently%20to%20provide%20an%20unbiased%20view.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20truly%20comprehend%20the%20vast%20economic%20potential%20brimming%20in%20India%2C%20visit%20its%20rural%20heartlands%20%E2%80%93%20like%20driving%20through%20the%20villages%20of%20Hubbali%20district%20in%20Karnataka.%20As%20you%20negotiate%20the%20twists%20and%20turns%20of%20the%20road%2C%20notice%20how%20the%20verdant%20landscape%20is%20punctuated%20with%20shops%2C%20now%20and%20then.%20A%20closer%20look%20will%20reveal%20barcodes%20displayed%20in%20plain%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20new%20addition%2C%20as%20shop%20owner%20Ishwargowda%20Basavanagowda%20Patil%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonday%20mornings%20are%20a%20busy%20time%20for%20him%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekirana%20%3C%2Fem%3E(general%20store)%20that%20he%20runs.%20But%20Ishwargowda%20seems%20unfazed%20by%20the%20slew%20of%20orders.%20He%E2%80%99s%20no%20longer%20required%20to%20ace%20mental%20mat