er%20Divya's%20classroom%20is%20one%20example%20of%20this%20%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-4-1727934307.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-4-1727934307-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-4-1727934307-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-4-1727934307-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-4-1727934307-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368497%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20the%20integration%20of%20smart%20TVs%20in%20classrooms%20in%20collaboration%20with%20LEAD%20Group%2C%20academics%20is%20no%20longer%20limited%20to%20the%20textbook.%20Teacher%20Divya%E2%80%99s%20classroom%20is%20one%20example%20of%20this%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20smart%20TVs%20in%20classrooms%2C%20digital%20tablets%20with%20pre-loaded%20lesson%20plans%20and%20tools%20for%20teachers%2C%20and%20school%20excellence%20kits%20that%20couple%20audio-visual%20learning%20with%20a%20kinesthetic%20approach%2C%20the%20duo%20is%20certain%20that%20learning%20is%20set%20to%20touch%20new%20horizons.%20Head%20Nandan%20testifies%20to%20this.%20%E2%80%9CA%20smart%20and%20interactive%20learning%20environment%20is%20created%20for%20the%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20they%20loving%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes!%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20Tanushree%2C%20a%20primary%20student.%20Today%2C%20she%20is%20particularly%20thrilled%20as%20her%20favourite%20fable%20%E2%80%98Magic%20Pot%E2%80%99%20got%20a%20whole%20new%20meaning%20through%20the%20audio-v