ed%20its%20presence.%20Today%2C%20even%20world%20governments%20are%20wary%20of%20its%20influence%20as%20could%20be%20perceived%20from%20reports%20of%20the%202016%20US%20Presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20internet%20can%20be%20a%20more%20dangerous%20world%20than%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20streets%20that%20women%20are%20often%20advised%20to%20avoid%20after%20sunset%E2%80%9D.%20Online%2C%20there%20is%20no%20sunrise%20or%20sunset%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20constant%2C%20deep%2C%20and%20dark%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20really%20have%20stringent%20laws%20yet.%20I%20have%20had%20victims%20showing%20me%20screenshots%20of%20conversations%20where%20the%20perpetrators%20are%20writing%20to%20them%3A%20%E2%80%98Do%20what%20you%20like%2C%20I%20know%20the%20Police%20will%20do%20nothing.%E2%80%99%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20like%20the%20police%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20do%20anything%3B%20it%20is%20just%20the%20volume%20of%20cases%20and%20the%20anonymity%20that%20online%20media%20allows%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nirali%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20the%20platforms%20are%20also%20not%20very%20prompt%20in%20collaborating%20and%20sharing%20information.%20We%20have%20been%20informed%20that%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20guidelines%2C%20if%20a%20woman%20or%20child%20is%20subjected%20to%20derogatory%20images%20being%20circulated%2C%20they%20can%20directly%20contact%20the%20grievance%20officer%20for%20assistance%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20getting%20responses%20is%20often%20challenging.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20report%20on%20the%20app%2C%20most%20of%20the%20time%20the%20response%20is%20that%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20violate%20their%20community%20guidelines%20or%20something%20similar.%20Even%20if%20an%20account%20is%20taken%20down%2C%20how%20long%20does%20it%20take%20for%20the%20perpetrator%20to%20create%20another%20one%3F%E2%80%9D%20Nirali%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202016-17%20I%20was%20part%20of%20a%20television%20show%20about%20tracking%20down%20these%20trolls%20who%20troll%20celebrities.%20Basically%2C%20the%20objective%20was%20to%20let%20the%20world%20know%20that%20anonymity%20is%20a%20myth%20online.%20There%20were%20times%20when%20we%20would%20be%20successful.%20I%E2%80%99d%20say%20it%E2%80%99s%2080-20%3B%2080%25%20of%20the%20time%20you%20can%2C%2020%25%20of%20the%20time%20it%E2%80%99s%20challenging%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nirali%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTechnology%20is%20improving.%20It%20is%20becoming%20much%20more%20difficult%20(to%20trace%20down%20perpetrators).%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20always%20possible%20to%20track%20them%20down%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20time-consuming%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAddressing%20cyberbullying%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Pritha%20and%20Priya%20agree%20that%20the%20first%20step%20for%20a%20woman%20to%20combat%20this%20menace%20is%20to%20confide%20in%20someone.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20talk%20to%20someone%2C%20that%20is%20primary%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pritha%20says.%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20for%20many%20people%2C%20reaching%20out%20and%20talking%20is%20essential%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priya%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENirali%20sees%20the%20blockade%20from%20societal%20stigma%20as%20a%20major%20problem%20in%20countering%20a%20menace%20that%20she%20believes%20is%20a%20pandemic.%20The%20NHRC%20data%20supports%20her%20claims.%20However%2C%20if%20you%20are%20a%20woman%20who%20has%20fallen%20victim%20to%20the%20malicious%20trolls%20that%20make%20the%20internet%20a%20dark%20place%2C%20there%20are%20certain%20steps%20you%20should%20take%2C%20starting%20with%20talking%20to%20someone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20never%20in%20the%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nirali%20says%2C%20explaining%20that%20sharing%20an%20incident%20with%20a%20loved%20one%20can%20help%20alleviate%20guilt%20and%20lead%20to%20concrete%20steps%20the%20victim%20can%20take.%20%E2%80%9CNothing%20is%20foolproof%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20acknowledges%20but%20asserts%20that%20women%20have%20no%20reason%20to%20feel%20guilty%20or%20ashamed%20because%20of%20a%20pervert%E2%80%99s%20actions%2C%20like%20morphing%20their%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20you%3B%20it%20is%20not%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pritha%20adds.%20As%20time%20goes%20on%2C%20the%20internet%20will%20increasingly%20dictate%20our%20lives%20more%20than%20the%20streets%20do.%20It%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20understand%20that%20harassment%20is%20harassment%2C%20and%20bullying%20is%20bullying%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20physical%20or%20virtual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyberbullying_11zon-1728365400.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyberbullying_11zon-1728365400.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyberbullying_11zon-1728365400-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyberbullying_11zon-1728365400-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyberbullying_11zon-1728365400-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyberbullying_11zon-1728365400-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369065%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EUnder%20India%E2%80%99s%20IT%20Rules%2C%20every%20social%20media%20platform%20is%20required%20to%20have%20a%20dedicated%20grievance%20redressal%20officer%20who%20is%20mandated%20to%20register%20a%20complaint%20within%2024%20hours.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20preventive%20steps%20that%20one%20can%20take%2C%20Nirali%20points%20out.%20The%20first%20is%20the%20utilisation%20of%20social%20media%20tools%20that%20are%20available%20at%20one%E2%80%99s%20disposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyone%20can%20be%20a%20victim%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20guilt%20or%20shame.%20To%20confide%20and%20then%20report%20about%20the%20crime%20are%20crucial%20in%20combatting%2C%20what%20Nirali%20aptly%20labels%20%E2%80%9Ca%20new%20age%20pandemic%E2%80%9D.%20With%20modern%20guidelines%20in%20place%2C%20any%20victim%20of%20any%20form%20of%20cyberbullying%20can%20register%20a%20complaint%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cybercrime.gov.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewww.cybercrime.gov.in%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20guidelines%20ensure%20that%20full%20anonymity%20is%20maintained%20throughout%20the%20entire%20redressal%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728318234000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyberbullying_11zon-1728365400.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D369032%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20digital%20landscape%20where%20words%20can%20inflict%20deep%20wounds%2C%20two%20women%20bravely%20share%20their%20harrowing%20experiences%20with%20cyberbullying.%20Their%20journeys%20not%20only%20highlight%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20awareness%20but%20also%20inspire%20others%20to%20find%20their%20voices%20and%20stand%20against%20the%20menace.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Arunava%20Banerjee%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F369032%2Fcyberbullying-in-india-women-how-to-address%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20Beauty%20Brand%20Turned%20100%20Million%20Bottles%20Into%20Opportunity%3A%20Helping%20To%20Empower%202000%20Waste%20Collectors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFeatured%20image%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ELeft%20image%3A%20Lakshmavva%3B%20Right%20image%3A%20Saraswati%20(Waste%20collector)%20%26amp%3B%20Jayanthi%20(waste%20collector)%20(L%20to%20R)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20plastic%20pollution%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20global%20crisis%2C%20significantly%20impacting%20marine%20life%20and%20human%20populations%20alike.%20India%20faces%20particular%20challenges%20due%20to%20inadequate%20waste%20management%20practices.%20Although%20efforts%20are%20underway%20to%20reduce%20plastic%20consumption%2C%20this%20alone%20is%20insufficient%20to%20tackle%20the%20escalating%20problem%20of%20plastic%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeadquartered%20in%20London%2C%20The%20Body%20Shop%20partnered%20with%20the%20startup%20%E2%80%98Plastics%20for%20Change%E2%80%99%20in%20India%20to%20launch%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebodyshop.in%2Fabout-us%2Factivism%2Fcommunity-trade-recycled-plastic%2Fe%2Fe00010%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECommunity%20Fair%20Trade%20Recycled%20Plastic%3C%2Fa%3E%20programme%20in%202019%2C%20aiming%20to%20incorporate%20community-traded%20recycled%20plastic%20into%20its%20best-selling%20products%20while%20helping%20to%20empower%20waste%20pickers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20part%20of%20the%20initiative%2C%20The%20Body%20Shop%20buys%20recycled%20plastic%20collected%20by%20waste%20collectors%20in%20a%20number%20of%20centres%20including%20Bengaluru%2C%20incorporating%20it%20into%20the%20packaging%20after%20thorough%20cleaning%20and%20converting%20it%20to%20recycled%20granules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Left%20image%20(L%20to%20R)%3A%20Lakshmavva%2C%20Gangavva%2C%20Saraswati%2C%20and%20Jayanthi%3B%20Right%20image%3A%20Shakunthala%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flh7-rt.googleusercontent.com%2Fdocsz%2FAD_4nXdCqw0lKR5M9ne9VF9mvnHSo886Zchoo3NPKdWblcC17TyIcuAd_xapehtBNMuX6dZDoFnq4qDD2Tb5LCzmhHCvcwht_rmB6VnOO6fcCFeW8rcXg-Iy3-ptJ6-xcD3AWP8nXtdhnsOUC0IHReYqEWHHK8nWLOybcR2skcP8ytteGaID4fA2oA%3Fkey%3DN9hf2spKjjJNMZc-gLRwCg%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELeft%20image%20(L%20to%20R)%3A%20Lakshmavva%2C%20Gangavva%2C%20Saraswati%2C%20and%20Jayanthi%3B%20Right%20image%3A%20Shakunthala%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Body%20Shop%20started%20by%20integrating%20Plastics%20For%20Change%20material%20into%20one%20product%20line%20(shampoos)%20and%20has%20now%20expanded%20to%2014%20product%20lines%2C%20including%20all%20PET%20bottles%20and%20jars.%20This%20expansion%20covers%20body%20and%20hair%20care%20products%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20skincare%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShriti%20Malhotra%2C%20Group%20CEO%20of%20Quest%20Retail%20The%20Body%20Shop%20India%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Body%20Shop%20and%20Plastics%20for%20Change%20collaborated%20with%20an%20ambitious%20goal%20of%20not%20just%20using%20recycled%20plastic%20but%20using%20plastic%20as%20a%20resource%20to%20uplift%20the%20lives%20of%20thousands%20of%20informal%20waste%20workers.%20Socially%2C%20the%20programme%20has%20created%20meaningful%20employment%20opportunities%20for%20marginalised%20communities.%20Importantly%2C%20over%2050%20percent%20of%20those%20involved%20in%20our%20partnership%20are%20women%2C%20contributing%20to%20gender%20equality%20in%20the%20workforce.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlastics%20for%20Change%20has%20been%20actively%20working%20to%20uplift%20the%20lives%20of%20waste%20collectors%20and%20their%20families.%20The%20programme%20also%20provides%20access%20to%20essential%20social%20services%20such%20as%20healthcare%2C%20education%2C%20and%20financial%20support%2C%20fostering%20holistic%20well-being%20within%20these%20communities.%20It%20empowers%20women%20waste%20collectors%20to%20become%20entrepreneurs%20and%20achieve%20financial%20independence%2C%20helping%20to%20break%20the%20cycle%20of%20poverty%20and%20promoting%20gender%20equality%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20fighting%20plastic%20pollution%20to%20championing%20waste%20collector%20rights%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20addressing%20plastic%20pollution%2C%20The%20Body%20Shop%20is%20collaborating%20with%20waste%20collectors%20%E2%80%94%20who%20are%20often%20the%20unsung%20heroes%20of%20waste%20management%20%E2%80%94%20to%20reshape%20the%20narrative%20surrounding%20waste%20management%20and%20improve%20their%20livelihoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20approximately%201.5%20million%20waste%20pickers%2C%20with%20around%20half%20a%20million%20being%20women%2C%20work%20tirelessly%20each%20day%20to%20clean%20the%20streets%20and%20cities.%20Unfortunately%2C%20many%20of%20these%20individuals%20face%20discrimination%20and%20endure%20poor%20working%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProject%20N.A.R.I%20(Nutrition.%20Ability.%20Retraining.%20Inclusion)%20was%20launched%20to%20address%20key%20challenges%20faced%20by%20waste%20collectors%2C%20especially%20women%2C%20who%20work%20in%20hazardous%20conditions%2C%20facing%20increased%20exposure%20to%20contaminated%20waste%20without%20adequate%20protective%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20initiative%2C%20100%20women%20waste%20collectors%20were%20provided%20PPE%20(personal%20protective%20equipment)%20kits%2C%20essential%20to%20reducing%20their%20health%20risks.%20Furthermore%2C%20they%20received%20daily%20meals%2C%20protein%2C%20and%20vitamin%20supplements%2C%20aimed%20at%20combating%20malnutrition%20and%20improving%20their%20overall%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20also%20promoted%20financial%20inclusion%20by%20facilitating%20access%20to%20banking%20systems%20and%20government%20schemes.%20For%20every%20kilogram%20of%20plastic%20traded%2C%20women%20received%20cash%20incentives%20directly