20from%20companies%20in%20Tanzania%20and%20Dubai.%20Instead%20of%20accepting%20these%20opportunities%2C%20Jagat%20aspired%20to%20run%20his%20own%20sustainable%20company%20in%20his%20native%20state%20of%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20job%20was%20very%20demanding%20and%20we%20were%20required%20to%20work%20for%2010%20to%2012%20hours.%20I%20would%20often%20discuss%20with%20my%20college%20friends%20Satyam%20Kumar%20and%20Nitish%20Verma%20about%20quitting%20jobs%20to%20build%20something%20meaningful%20of%20our%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20Jagat%20and%20his%20college%20friends%20started%20researching%20various%20issues%20that%20needed%20their%20attention.%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20our%20work%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20put%20Bihar%20on%20the%20world%20map.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20it%20hit%20us%20that%20since%20Hajipur%20is%20known%20for%20its%20banana%20production%2C%20why%20don%E2%80%99t%20we%20focus%20on%20banana%20waste%20%E2%80%94%20an%20issue%20that%20all%20of%20us%20grew%20up%20seeing%20on%20our%20fields%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Ftaruwar-4-1727440526.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22After%20extracting%20fibre%20from%20banana%20tree%20waste%2C%20the%20startup%20makes%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Ftaruwar-4-1727440526.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Ftaruwar-4-1727440526-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Ftaruwar-4-1727440526-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Ftaruwar-4-1727440526-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebet